
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-opsec-routing-capabilities-03.txt'>
    <title>"Routing Control Plane Security Capabilities", Zhao Ye, Miao Fuyou, Ross  Callon</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-opsec-routing-capabilities-03.txt</link>
    <description>The document lists the security capabilities needed for the routing control plane of an IP infrastructure to support the practices defined in Operational Security Current Practices. In particular this includes capabilities for route filtering, for authentication of routing protocol packets, and for ensuring resource availability for control functions.</description>
    <dc:date>2007-06-14T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
